name: Birthday Gift Bag Kit
description:
We have put together these amazing gift bag kits to make it   easy for anyone to give gifts anytime.

This kit includes 3 gift bags with 6 sheets of birthday tissue paper and 3 matching gift cards. 

These classy square-bottomed gift bags measure 8"(w)x8"(d)x10"(h). They are made of high-quality glossy white paper that doesn't rip when inserting the gift and have sturdy nylon handles. 

Tissue features: 3 different designs of birthday tissue

The cards are blank inside for quick and easy messages and can attach to the gift bag.

The kit comes packaged in a clear zip bag and is shipped in a USPS Priority Flat Rate Envelope.
